data.description: Gardeners Delight with citrus & fruit trees in abundance. Large lot with plenty of room for vegetable garden, flower garden.  Elegant black rod iron fence front yard with:  Lemon, Lime, Mandarin, Orange, 3 crape myrtles,& Agave plants. Park size fenced backyard with: 3 Pistachio, 2 Cherry,1 Nectarine, 1 Apricot, 1 Peach. Large/wide parking area side of home room for at least 6 vehicles, RV, boat. If a large well manicured yard is high on your list, this home will not disappoint.   Large family room, big eat in kitchen, oversized laundry room. 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms.
